![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/da33441c-fd7e-4512-ab05-213c462b0b5a)

Still possible to delete the sub manifests manually with `skopeo delete docker://.../my-image@sha256:bafedd65..` :

![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/0f58198b-d6b4-45d8-9d6e-296301436714)

</details>


